cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper is about face recognition and template adaptation using deep convolutional networks and linear SVMs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of metric learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves multimedia analysis and retrieval, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses negative set construction, which is related to information retrieval and could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper discusses the performance evaluation of face recognition systems, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
